title: Refrigerator Door Shelf Retainer Bar End Cap - Left Side
description: Refrigerator Door Shelf Retainer Bar End Cap - Left Side ★★★★★ ★★★★★ 4 Reviews PartSelect Number PS429667 Manufacturer Part Number 240311501 This is a replacement end cap for your freezer or refrigerator shelf retainer bar. You will need a flat blade screwdriver to complete this repair. To replace this part, remove the retainer bar by popping the end caps out of place. Use the screwdriver to pop out the individual end cap you are replacing. Secure the new one in place with the locking tabs and re-insert the retainer bar.
